data.description: This beautiful Atlantic Beach home is nestled in the Royal Palms area. 1 mile from the Ocean, a few blocks from Jack Rustle Park, Howell Park. Atlantic Beach Elementary. Shopping and dining within minutes of the location. A short drive to the stadium for sporting events. The wishing well is a custom BBQ Grill. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, living room and den with a fireplace. Kitchen with breakfast area, Separate dining area. Utility room with a washer and dryer. Storage shed in back that conveys with the property. This is your chance to live at the Beach in comfort. The home is in move in ready condition. The seller will do no repairs. Upgraded electrical panel.  New Vinyl waterproof flooring. The roof is approx. 6 years old. The Air conditioner is the same age and just serviced.
